{"tid":94614,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[暗瘡jj] 中藥定西藥？","createTime":"2017-01-25T10:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T20:42:26.000Z","uid":74630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"600d530ef74e9bb279da31d49464242921fcfe81","tid":94614,"uid":74630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n近排爆瘡爆得好勁，終於決定睇醫生搞搞佢<br />\n我揀咗西醫睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢開咗藥膏同a酸比我食，醫生話a酸會影響到個肝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋搽藥膏搽到塊面好乾好乾，瘋狂甩皮，嘴爆擦得勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但幾見效，要食8個星期<br />\n<br />\n但屋企人覺得食太多西藥會好孱，想我食中藥<br />\n我啊妹仲嚴重過我，佢食咗中藥應該兩個月度，都好咗少少<br />\n<br />\n想問下你地意見，應該繼續食西藥定轉中藥好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ae08b6358494972a4f97f25dfa660e3cd440c9","tid":94614,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"中醫 <br />\n仲要努力戒口"},{"pid":"9700ee1da874466d9981fa1c0cc285360ba92a44","tid":94614,"uid":62894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"中醫斷到尾 <br />\n同埋西藥對肝好差 一停又會爆返"},{"pid":"422c07e4be488fd1e1c509f6f5cc02c4166e3a2d","tid":94614,"uid":74630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫 <br />\n仲要努力戒口</blockquote><br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db0166c0a381e50bde5c786261c2db27933cb0f","tid":94614,"uid":74630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫斷到尾 <br />\n同埋西藥對肝好差 一停又會爆返</blockquote><br />\n但食食下西藥又停再中藥都可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce378ee18929cd2fb8bb5680235feb4e247b64d","tid":94614,"uid":55379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"用番梘 手工梘沖涼<br />\n用天然沐浴露<br />\n食就食蘑菇精華"},{"pid":"37908fbc23724218c2a99ea19c794508629dc00e","tid":94614,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"西藥效力快 中藥够溫和"},{"pid":"36f990f35f92e2f7d92e52fd6886582272e535f1","tid":94614,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"之前有一排戒左口<br />\n但d瘡都係係咁爆<br />\n所以慢慢都有戒，因為覺得唔係好關事<br />\n<br />\n但自從我買過一set新既潔面用品之後<br />\n呢兩個禮拜都未爆瘡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3p7Mc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3p7Mc7.jpg&h=39546880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我懷疑係因為之前做野壓力大，改變左自己既膚質先至會係咁生<br />\n依家用左acnes d產品，可能佢真係慢慢將你d皮膚變番好d<br />\n冇咁易生<br />\n<br />\n拿，支爽膚水係咁講既<br />\n<img src=\"https://n