ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西藥效力快 中藥够溫和</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想屌你"},{"pid":"94287feece99a6f1ac8658392d45fd0e267ea4e7","tid":94614,"uid":74630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫雖然慢 但3個月肯戒口一定有改善，改善完一定要keep住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加油呀Ching，我都仲戒緊口</blockquote><br />\n戒口呢一part真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唯有當減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你 我會比心機戒口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502502b22641879277fde49a7a1eee63e51b2e45","tid":94614,"uid":74630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中醫斷到尾 <br />\n同埋西藥對肝好差 一停又會爆返</blockquote><br />\n但食食下西藥又停再中藥都可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以 你去睇中醫果陣同佢講返就得<br />\n潔面都有關係既 但如果你話爆得勁我諗睇中醫調理返會好D<br />\n利申 之前都爛得好犀利 舊年食中藥到而家順滑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有排有天然洗面膏洗面 真係好咗好多<br />\n依家食西藥都好咗少少<br />\n如果可以轉 咁我轉睇中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事食到孱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒你 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05aa3a72a7244720f323db1e49132751d688fdd","tid":94614,"uid":15693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"66997dcadb5e3d2f2cbf9611859d6199aae47ff5","tid":94614,"uid":15693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中</blockquote><br />\n中醫"},{"pid":"0bc04b881b1c956b66c0ba6fee28f41e297f307e","tid":94614,"uid":23639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"西藥治標中藥治本"},{"pid":"2bae89b82b77031cd98f636ade2fe9d9bc4fc7f3","tid":94614,"uid":4218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"我以前都食過a酸 好傷肝 而且仲會爆菊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為抽乾哂身體水份 <br />\n食完好過一排又番發<br />\n而且食過a酸數年內拕B 好似有副作用<br />\n<br />\n最好食中藥 不過藥帶3分毒 你都要睇住時間黎食<br />\n<br />\n我之前有段時間戒左陣肉 有短期布緯 早瞓 食淮山粥 飲黑豆煲水-不加調味（可以食埋黑豆-可調味） 皮膚有大改進<br />\n如果你有少少錢 可以加埋epionce lytic既產品 <br />\n冇錢可以試下cetaphil 既洗面 兩樣我同朋友用過都有效<br />\n仲有個傳聞work既acne用品 可以睇下 <a href=\"http://www.acne.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.acne.org&d=KS63R3rJpaSDpfNIyduusgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=99662f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.acne.org</a> <br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e4f856780a2099720629b8925dfa17ddee0d97","tid":94614,"uid":62894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中醫斷到尾 <br />\n同埋西藥對肝好差 一停又會爆返</blockquote><br />\n但食食下西藥又停再中藥都可以？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以 你去睇中醫果陣同佢講返就得<br />\n潔面都有關係既 但如果你話爆得勁我諗睇中醫調理返會好D<br />\n利申 之前都爛得好犀利 舊年食中藥到而家順滑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有排有天然洗面膏洗面 真係好咗好多<br />\n依家食西藥都好咗少少<br />\n如果可以轉 咁我轉睇中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事食到孱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒你 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n孱都唔算大件事 我有屋企人以前後生果陣睇某皮膚科名醫<br />\n佢咪係咁開A酸西藥比佢<br />\n後來都覺得唔對路停左<br />\n到而家老左肝有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中醫係慢 但比D耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"603b6eea4c7dbbe7a07aa72e823ed77b14a52e76","tid":94614,"uid":3858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"有圖 慎入！！<br />\n小弟塊面好幾年都係咁 <br />\n是味都要睇中醫 先有夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/fT8HkY2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfT8HkY2.jpg&d=KS63R3rJpaSDpfNIyduusgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=759103ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/fT8HkY2.jpg</a><a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233629_98cf262b00245e41dbf04d9b32ec5b39.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233629_98cf262b00245e41dbf04d9b32ec5b39.jpg&d=KS63R3rJpaSDpfNIyduusgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=bd4eaf0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233629_98cf262b00245e41dbf04d9b32ec5b39.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"196f446619f4fc892dbd172d8775ea3b10eaca73","tid":94614,"uid":3858,"like":0,"dislike":0,